Package: hirisplexr
Type: Package
Title: From PLINK to HIrisPlex
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Andrea Giardina [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Andrea Giardina <r@andreagiardina.com>
Description: Read PLINK 1.9 binary datasets (BED/BIM/FAM) and generate the CSV
    files required by the Erasmus MC HIrisPlex / HIrisPlex-S webtool. It maps
    PLINK alleles to the webtool's required 'rsID_Allele' columns (0/1/2/NA).
    No external tools (e.g., PLINK CLI) are required.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/agiardina/hirisplexr
BugReports: https://github.com/agiardina/hirisplexr/issues
Depends: R (>= 3.6)
Imports:
    BEDMatrix,
    data.table,
    utils
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
VignetteBuilder: knitr
